Shagit
A simple web-app based on Sinatra for managing local git repositories
(c) 2010 Martin Gajdos. All rights reserved.

Introduction
------------

Dependencies
------------
* Sinatra
* Rack

Installation
------------

You will need a working installation of Ruby 1.8.x, RubyGems >= 1.3.5 and git.

Clone the repository:
# git clone git://github.com/unabatede/shagit.git

Install the Sinatra & rack-flash gems:
# gem install sinatra nakajima-rack-flash

Run it (you should consider other options for production deployment):
# cd shagit
# ruby shagit.rb -e production